    "name": "Deepest Dungeons",
    "steam_appid": 3137960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Deepest Dungeons</strong>这款融合了<strong>Rogue-like</strong>与提取机制的冒险游戏中，你将深入一个不断变化的迷宫。每次探险，迷宫都会发生变化，考验你的意志，让你一步步踏入更深沉的黑暗之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演一位年轻的冒险者，响应国王的召唤，前往地底夺回被神秘怪物掠走的珍贵符文。只有胸中的勇气和沿途收集的装备，你必须在这片危险无情的地下世界中生存，探索更深层的区域，夺回失落的珍宝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137960/extras/f04344a2ed71c4b2d5772d73f41ca2cf.avif?t=1744102872\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险的过程中，你将遭遇强大的怪物、致命的陷阱，并发现隐藏的宝藏。想要深入更低层的迷宫，你需要找到散落其中的特殊钥匙。与此同时，你还能获得稀有道具与装备，提升你的生存能力，为即将面对的挑战做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137960/extras/acd376cab6652d5025dbe276a012d559.avif?t=1744102872\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地牢都是一个独特的迷宫，充满了各自的挑战与危险。越往深处，迷宫就越庞大，也更加复杂，需要你巧妙运用发现的工具和智慧来寻找出口。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137960/extras/4a24bed87c2f20b2b122b8a4297a5d2c.avif?t=1744102872\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候，你会遇到通往地面的出口。此时，你需要做出选择：返回地表，在<strong>Stashbox</strong>（储藏箱）中存储进度并调整策略，还是继续深入地下，冒险挑战更高的风险，换取更丰厚的奖励？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137960/extras/c773f5ebc5e64865a00fa90ea199be56.avif?t=1744102872\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你会找到过去探险者遗留下来的装备和道具。这些物品不仅能增强你的战斗力，还能为你提供关键的生存优势，让你更好地穿梭于错综复杂的迷宫之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137960/extras/8f5ebd418bb85d724a87b3b8e157a087.avif?t=1744102872\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地牢中潜伏着危险的怪物和致命的陷阱。作为一名毫无经验的乡村冒险者，你必须认真对待每一场战斗。越深入地下，怪物就越强大，威胁也越严峻。保持警惕——每次遭遇都可能是你最后一次挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137960/extras/955569aa5ac932f2d8e0f231da62e525.avif?t=1744102872\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但死亡并不是终点。尽管你会失去当前的进度，但<strong>Stashbox</strong>中的物品会保留下来，帮助你在下一次探险中更进一步。学习、适应，然后再次深入迷宫——每一次失败都会让你变得更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而对于征服地底深渊的玩家来说，新的挑战正在等待着你：<strong>New Game Plus</strong>（新游戏+）模式，让你在更高的难度下再次踏入地牢，面对全新的威胁</p>",
